casebody.data:
Rosa PEREZ, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
Joseph BATOR, Jane Bator, Jose Parraguez and Rosalyne (Rocio) Parraguez, Defendants-Respondents. C-811 September Term 2017
080590 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 4, 2018

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION.

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001264-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
